11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_RECEIVE_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_RECEIVE_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
17#include "logging/rtc_event_log/rtc_stream_config.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21class RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig final : public RtcEvent {
22 public:
23 static constexpr Type kType = Type::AudioReceiveStreamConfig;
24
25 explicit RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig(
26 std::unique_ptr<rtclog::StreamConfig> config);
27 ~RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig() override;
28
29 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
30 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return true; }
31
32 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig> Copy() const;
33
34 const rtclog::StreamConfig& config() const { return *config_; }
35
36 private:
37 RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig(
38 const RtcEventAudioReceiveStreamConfig& other);
39
40 const std::unique_ptr<const rtclog::StreamConfig> config_;
41};
42
43struct LoggedAudioRecvConfig {
44 LoggedAudioRecvConfig() = default;
45 LoggedAudioRecvConfig(int64_t timestamp_us, const rtclog::StreamConfig config)
46 : timestamp_us(timestamp_us), config(config) {}
47
48 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_us; }
49 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_us / 1000; }
50
51 int64_t timestamp_us;
52 rtclog::StreamConfig config;
53};
54
55} // namespace webrtc
56
57#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_RECEIVE_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
